  "instructions": [
    "Slice the beef shin into thin strips.",
    "Dice the onions, carrots, and tomatoes.",
    "Chop the garlic finely.",
    "Add olive oil to a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat. Add thyme and bay leaves, sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add sliced beef, cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in diced onions, carrots, and tomatoes, then garlic. Cook for an additional 3-4 minutes.",
    "Turn the heat down to medium-low and let it simmer for another 20 minutes or until the meat is tender and flavorful.",
    "Season with salt and pepper according to your taste.",
    "Serve hot."
